						<summary>

						<p>Records a gift of land by purchase from Śēnāvaruchchāṇi by Irāmayaṉ for the daily offering of a garland to the deity for his (donor's) own well-being. The date of the record <hi rend="italic">viz.,</hi> 23rd year of reign, Kuṁbha, śu. 3. Sunday, Pūśam is irregular.</p>						

